tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE call_logs (
  call_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  caller_number VARCHAR(10),
  receiver_number VARCHAR(10),
  call_duration INT,
  call_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  call_type VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE call_logs (
  call_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  caller_id INT,
  receiver_id INT,
  call_duration INT,
  call_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE call_logs (
    call_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    caller_id UUID,
    receiver_id UUID,
    call_duration INT,
    call_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE customer (
    customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    registration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE call_history (
    history_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    call_id UUID,
    caller_id UUID,
    receiver_id UUID,
    call_duration INT,
    call_time TIMESTAMP
);
